<div style="background:#161b22;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:2rem auto">
<p style="color:#9eaab6;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.25rem">Federal Rules Committee</p>
<p style="color:#e6edf3;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem">This research supports two accepted suggestions to the Advisory Committee on Bankruptcy Rules: <a href="https://www.uscourts.gov/forms-rules/records-rules-committees/suggestions/dan-brown-26-bk-3" style="color:#58a6ff">Suggestion 26-BK-3</a> and <a href="https://www.uscourts.gov/forms-rules/records-rules-committees/suggestions/dan-brown-26-bk-5" style="color:#58a6ff">Suggestion 26-BK-5</a></p>
<p style="color:#9eaab6;font-size:0.8rem;margin:0">Proposing automated <a href="https://section1328.org" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="Section 1328 Discharge - Open Bankruptcy Project">Section 1328</a>(f) <a href="https://dischargebar.org" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="Bankruptcy Discharge Bar - Open Bankruptcy Project">discharge bar</a> screening and <a href="https://openbankruptcyproject.org/rule-9037/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="Rule 9037 SSN Redaction - Open Bankruptcy Project">Rule 9037</a> SSN redaction in federal bankruptcy courts</p>
</div>
